videos.headline: Wisconsin's Peavy slices up the field 46 yards for a TD
videos.description: Wisconsin's Jazz Peavy evades every Northwestern Wildcat defender 46 yards to the end zone, widening the gap 10-0.

videos.headline: Northwestern responds to Wisconsin with flawless TD pass
videos.description: Northwestern QB Clayton Thorson connects with Austin Carr in the end zone for a 13-yard touchdown to cut Northwestern's deficit to three.
